--- ftd.code:
if: $fpm.dark-mode
text: $body
lang: $lang
color: #4D4D4D
width: fill
size: 17
line-height: 25
padding-top: 10
padding-left: 20
padding-bottom: 10
padding-right: 20
background-color: #2b303b
border-top-radius if $caption is null: 4
border-bottom-radius: 4
border-width: 1
overflow-x: auto

--- ftd.code:
